body:
### What changes were proposed in this pull request?
add tests for:
1, `DataFrame.drop` with empty column;
2, `DataFrame.drop` with column names containing dot;


### Why are the changes needed?
for better test coverage, the two UTs were once broken in [SPARK-39895](https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-39895), and then fixed in [SPARK-42444](https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-42444)


### Does this PR introduce _any_ user-facing change?
no, test-only


### How was this patch tested?
added UTs
